# Banana bread recipe 

## Ingredients 
- 3 Bananas 
- 100g sugar 
- 70g sunflower oil 
- 200g chopped chocolate 
- 225g plain flour 
- 2 heaped teaspoons baking powder 
- 2 teaspoons cinnamon 

## Method
- Mash bananas 
- Mix oil and sugar into mashed bananas 
- Add plain flour, baking powder and cinnamon and mix 
- Fold in chocolate 
- OPTIONAL: Slice a banana lengthways and lay across the top 
- Bake at 180 degrees C for 1 hour. Cover with foil halfway through
